title: What’s More Likely & TNF Preview
itunes:title: What’s More Likely & TNF Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling, Gregg Rosenthal & Colleen Wolfe – discuss all the latest news from around the NFL including a falling out between the Rams front office and former Rams running back Eric Dickerson. Then the heroes dive into a rousing games of “What’s More Likely” before previewing the Thursday night game between the Vikings and the Cowboys.
